2000-07-11 21:56  ftobin

	* lib/GnuPG/Handles.pm, lib/GnuPG/Interface.pm,
	lib/GnuPG/Options.pm, t/MyTestSpecific.pm, t/clearsign.t,
	t/decrypt.t, t/detach_sign.t, t/encrypt.t,
